    Column I

    Column II




    (A)

    (P)
    $$\delta ({P_0}) = 0$$



    (B)
    $$(\mu-1)t=\lambda/4$$

    (Q)
    $$\delta ({P_1}) = 0$$



    (C)
    $$(\mu-1)t=\lambda/2$$

    (R)
    $$I({P_1}) = 0$$



    (D)
    $$(\mu-1)t=3\lambda/4$$

    (S)
    $$I({P_0}) > I({P_1})$$





    (T)
    $$I({P_2}) > I({P_1})$$

